/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a car on the road, giving a driver's eye view of the scene. The street is lined with lush green trees and bushes, adding a touch of nature to the urban landscape. Tall buildings rise in the background, their towering presence a testament to the city's architectural prowess. Overhead, power lines crisscross against the backdrop of a cloudy sky, a common sight in many urban areas. The colors in the image are predominantly green, gray, and brown, reflecting the blend of nature and urban development.
